Der Clou!
=========================

Original version by:
	neo Software Produktions GmbH

Port by:
	Vasco Alexandre da Silva Costa <vasco.costa AT gmail.com>
	
Portmaster Version : https://github.com/christianhaitian/PortMaster 

	- Cebion https://github.com/Cebion
	
Special Thanks to: kloptops



To compile:
===========

git clone  https://github.com/vcosta/derclou.git
cd dercloud
make -j8


Instructions:
=============

To run the game start Der Clou .sh from your ports folder 

Controls:
=============

A			 = Enter / Fire
B 			 = Exit Menu
Select 		 = Open Save Menu

